   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>The attached git format-patch series implements the "cards" mockup described
here: <a href="http://lists.openhatch.org/pipermail/devel/2011-September/002368.html">http://lists.openhatch.org/pipermail/devel/2011-September/002368.html</a>

In theory, the "cards" could use some color, but I think it's actually good
enough to ship as-is.

I made one change on top of what's in the screenshot: the card titles are pale
if and only if the mission is not completed yet.

Requesting review, on the code changes and/or the design changes. If someone
likes this, please feel free to just deploy it.</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
